    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, very formal. But to really make the scene feel gritty and authentic to the period, can you have Sterling get a bit more descriptive? He should probably mention the actual appearance of the people they're encountering and how their \"raw\" or \"uncontrolled\" nature contrasts with the discipline of his men. I want the audience to really feel his sense of superiority when he looks at them.",
